.rule_6_7_4_ensure_ntp_uses_version_4

Reference: Guide](https://www.juniper.net/documentation/en_US/junos/information-
products/pathway-pages/system-basics/time-management.html)
Requirement 10.4

Remediation: Configure each External NTP Server to use NTP Version 4 using the following commands
under the [edit system ntp] hierarchy:
[edit system ntp]
user@host#set server <Servers IP>  version 4

.